WEBVTT

00:04.000 --> 00:05.850
没阳光了 快回去
We're losing the light Go back

00:09.840 --> 00:10.910
你
You.

00:11.370 --> 00:12.570
这是你的房间吧?
Is it your cell?

00:18.830 --> 00:21.770
你准备越狱 斯科菲尔德先生
You are breaking out of this prison, Mr. Scofield.

00:21.780 --> 00:23.160
你得带上我
And you're taking me with you.

00:23.170 --> 00:24.440
那么
So with this deal

00:24.910 --> 00:27.900
他们到底想从我这得到些什么?
what specifically are they expecting from me?

00:27.910 --> 00:29.410
他们想知道所有的事
They need to know everything.

00:29.420 --> 00:31.470
他们要确认你的消息可靠
They want to confirm that you have viable,

00:31.480 --> 00:32.580
并且能够帮助他们定罪
incriminating information

00:32.590 --> 00:34.890
还要你乖乖地做个证人
and that you can be a cooperative witness.

00:34.960 --> 00:36.150
给我看看照片
Show me the pictures.

00:36.160 --> 00:37.740
没照片看 兄弟
I can't show you the pictures, man.

00:38.620 --> 00:40.060
她死了 迈克
She's dead, Michael.

00:41.880 --> 00:44.240
不是说好了 你最好别来这吗
I thought we agreed it was best for you to not come here.

00:44.250 --> 00:46.190
我得知道这次耽搁会有多大影响
I need to know how this delay is going to affect things.

00:46.200 --> 00:47.740
再给我四天
four more days

00:47.890 --> 00:49.510
要是我能离开这的话
If I'm out of here by then

00:49.760 --> 00:51.340
我仍然能够做到
I can still do it.

00:51.360 --> 00:52.830
我会转告那两兄弟的
I'll let the brothers know.

01:20.130 --> 01:21.330
迈克
Michael.

01:22.600 --> 01:23.680
我看起来怎么样
You like this?

01:24.600 --> 01:25.690
不错
Yeah.

01:25.880 --> 01:27.690
今天是个特殊的日子
It's a special occasion.

01:28.290 --> 01:29.000
我爸爸今天要来看我
My dad's coming today,

01:29.010 --> 01:31.310
我在等他过来
so I'm just gonna wait here till he shows up.

01:34.450 --> 01:35.490
蛮精神的
You look sharp.

01:36.410 --> 01:36.580
谢谢
Thanks.

01:36.590 --> 01:38.620
斯科菲尔德 有访客
Scofield , you have a vistor

01:46.400 --> 01:47.960
-LJ 他还 ? -还活着
-LJ. Is he ? -Alive.

01:49.910 --> 01:51.450
又给了我们4天时间
Giving us four more days.

01:51.650 --> 01:53.050
好
Okay, good.

01:53.970 --> 01:55.310
听着 在交易地点
Listen, back at the exchange point,

01:55.320 --> 01:57.080
我看到了3个尸体袋
I saw three body bags.

01:57.330 --> 01:57.980
你 我 还有LJ的
You, me and LJ,

01:57.990 --> 01:59.890
他们没想放过我们
we weren't getting out of there alive.

02:02.780 --> 02:04.810
我不会再鲁莽行事了
That's the last time I get caught flatfooted.

02:06.410 --> 02:08.080
那就去做你该做的事 林肯
Then do what you got to do, Linc.

02:09.090 --> 02:11.680
我会管好我这里的事 行吗?
As long as I take care of my end, right?

02:12.060 --> 02:14.700
迈克我知道莎拉的事 你很生我的气 但
Michael, I know you're angry with me about Sara, but

02:14.710 --> 02:15.880
你说谎了
You lied.

02:16.800 --> 02:18.110
我不得不说谎
I had to lie.

02:20.700 --> 02:23.130
你儿子是我侄子
Your son is my nephew,

02:25.130 --> 02:27.250
我会为他做一切的
and there's nothing I wouldn't do for him.

02:29.380 --> 02:30.650
但显然
But apparently

02:31.970 --> 02:34.240
你认为我只在意自己的事
apparently you only think I only care about myself.

02:34.250 --> 02:35.540
我知道你关心的不是自己
I know you don't care about yourself,

02:35.550 --> 02:37.800
你关心的是莎拉
but you cared about Sara.

02:37.910 --> 02:39.000
你爱她
You loved her.

02:39.330 --> 02:40.460
我很遗憾
And I'm sorry.

02:41.070 --> 02:42.040
但LJ是我儿子
But LJ's my son.

02:42.050 --> 02:43.960
我 我不能让他有事
I-I couldn't let anything happen to him.

02:43.970 --> 02:45.100
你知道的
You know that.

02:46.740 --> 02:48.270
你利用了我 林肯
You used me, Linc.

02:49.910 --> 02:52.570
你这点和组织倒是挺像的
So I guess you and the Company have something in common.

02:59.450 --> 03:00.450
我不知道他在哪
I don't know where he is.

03:00.460 --> 03:02.720
我所有号码都试了一遍
I have tried every number I have.

03:02.990 --> 03:06.560
听着 我会再去总部查查
Listen I will check back in headquarters

03:06.570 --> 03:07.930
看他们怎么说
and see what they say.

03:09.950 --> 03:11.040
别管了
Never mind.

03:11.570 --> 03:12.710
我找到他了
I found him.

03:20.540 --> 03:22.400
蓝色卡特
Carter Blue Label.

03:22.890 --> 03:23.550
你虽然出身平凡
You always had such

03:23.560 --> 03:26.850
却很有品味嘛
high-end taste for a girl from Wheeling.

03:28.220 --> 03:29.620
还不是用我的钱
Since I paid for it

03:31.080 --> 03:33.560
你知道我有多么痛恨四处奔波 格雷琴
You know how much I hate to travel, Gretchen

03:35.560 --> 03:39.440
但是考虑到这里的状况 我不得不破例来一趟
but considering the mess down here, I made an exception.

03:39.450 --> 03:41.500
在我来之前 这里就混乱不堪
It was a mess before I got here.

03:41.510 --> 03:43.220
那现在是时候清理下了
And it's time to clean it up.

03:43.430 --> 03:45.190
今天就做个了结吧
We're ending this today.

03:50.870 --> 03:52.320
来硬的
Bang and burn.

03:55.530 --> 03:57.200
将军 我已经分析过了
General, that was analyzed.

03:57.260 --> 03:58.010
如此做法
What you're asking for

03:58.020 --> 03:59.870
太危险了 更何况
is too dangerous, not to mention

03:59.880 --> 04:02.410
时间上根本来不及
next to impossible with the given time frame.

04:02.410 --> 04:02.960
我认为
I remember

04:02.970 --> 04:06.550
当一大笔钱汇到你海外帐户的时候
a substantial wire transfer to an offshore account

04:06.560 --> 04:08.770
那就意味着我们的字典里没有"不可能"
that took the word"impossible"

04:08.860 --> 04:11.700
难道说
out of the equation or tell me,

04:12.490 --> 04:14.340
是我选错了人?
did I hire the wrong person?

04:16.390 --> 04:19.900
提醒你做事要三思 也是我的工作
I am doing my job when I tell you to seriously reconsider.

04:20.580 --> 04:23.800
那现在 我要按我的意思办了
And now, I have to do my job.

04:26.600 --> 04:28.720
我不是花钱让你做我顾问的
I don't pay you to be my advisor.

04:29.060 --> 04:30.420
你只是执行任务的
You're my operator.

04:30.440 --> 04:33.210
你收到命令 就得完成任务
You have your instructions, now get it done.

04:33.770 --> 04:35.200
不然的话
Beuse if you don't,

04:35.870 --> 04:38.350
你上次在摩苏尔(伊拉克北部城市)
I'll make what happened to you in Mosul

04:38.420 --> 04:40.710
遭受的一切就只是个开头罢了
feel like a massage.

04:44.310 --> 04:46.110
这件事是个错误 格雷琴
This was a big mistake, Gretchen.

04:46.850 --> 04:48.840
你不能老来这里
You can't make a habit of coming to Sona.

04:49.270 --> 04:50.310
我不会了
I won't.

04:50.740 --> 04:52.860
因为我们要来硬的了
Because we're going with the bang and burn .

04:55.310 --> 04:56.690
那等于自寻死路
That's suicide.

04:57.810 --> 04:59.030
我们还有时间呢
We have more time.

04:59.730 --> 05:02.270
我老板想快点完事
My boss wants things to move a bit faster.

05:02.280 --> 05:04.130
那你告诉他这样行不通
Well, tell him you can't pull it off.

05:04.380 --> 05:05.710
这么干我可能会被杀了的
I might get killed if we do this.

05:05.720 --> 05:07.930
不这么干我就会被干掉了
And I might get killed if we don't.

05:08.440 --> 05:09.120
你和我之间
Between you and me,

05:09.130 --> 05:11.250
你认为我会更关心谁?
who do you think I care about more?

05:11.770 --> 05:13.260
看着我 詹姆斯
Look at me, James.

05:13.460 --> 05:15.850
看看我有多认真
See if you can tell how serious I am.

05:16.370 --> 05:17.780
如果你不配合
If you don't play ball,

05:17.790 --> 05:20.360
你就等着把牢坐穿吧
I will leave you in Sona to rot.

05:20.970 --> 05:22.190
我保证
I promise.

05:22.930 --> 05:24.550
5点钟 准备好
Be ready by 5:00.

05:24.560 --> 05:26.060
那时行动
That's when it happens.

05:26.400 --> 05:27.980
一起行动
Everybody goes.

05:28.700 --> 05:30.150
斯科菲尔德如何处置?
What about Scofield?

05:31.180 --> 05:32.400
杀了他
Kill him.

