如果有人看到我们俩说话 你知道后果的
You know the consequences if I'm seen talking to you?

06:37.860 --> 06:40.340
军队正在加固所有门窗上的铁栏
The military's reinforcing the bars on all the windows.

06:40.590 --> 06:41.820
能否和长官谈谈
Can you talk to the colonel,

06:41.830 --> 06:43.820
让他暂缓几天?
get him to postpone that for a few days? .

06:44.200 --> 06:45.260
经你昨天这么一闹
After your performance yesterday,

06:45.270 --> 06:47.250
我已经没有发言权了
I have no further sway with the colonel.

06:47.320 --> 06:48.560
那我恐怕你是选了条
Well, then I'm afraid you've brokered your way

06:48.570 --> 06:51.050
根本不可能成功的路来逃生
into an escape plan that no longer exists.

06:54.400 --> 06:55.540
我有办法了
I have an idea.

06:55.550 --> 06:56.950
勒齐
Lechero

06:57.960 --> 06:59.340
等我消息
Wait to hear from me.

07:00.310 --> 07:01.310
怎么了
What?

07:06.170 --> 07:10.080
有些人不想再付保护费给你了
Some of the men don't feel the need to pay their debts anymore.

07:10.550 --> 07:11.950
已经一周了
It's been one week, man,

07:11.970 --> 07:13.490
我们已经少了三个人了
and we lost three men.

07:13.730 --> 07:16.440
现在 如果我们要控制索纳监狱 我们需要人手
Now, if we gonna keep Sona, we're gonna need numbers.

07:17.450 --> 07:20.550
这里我现在谁都不信 尤其是现在
I don't trust nobody here right now especially now.

07:22.770 --> 07:24.310
我只想用自己人
I work with the men I have.

07:25.140 --> 07:26.320
是吗 兄弟?
Really, brother?

07:27.380 --> 07:28.050
你和我
You, me

07:28.060 --> 07:30.320
还有那个废物 就靠我们三个?
and the gimp over there, we gonna run this place?

07:31.460 --> 07:33.130
我想带上克里斯托巴
I want to bring on Cristobal.

07:34.550 --> 07:35.900
他靠得住 老大
He's solid, man.

07:35.920 --> 07:37.800
又是戴伦犹太人
One of them Darrien ghetto boys.

07:41.820 --> 07:42.970
那就带上他吧
Bring him up.

07:44.880 --> 07:46.370
但是我不能保证你什么
But I promise you nothing.

07:52.180 --> 07:54.140
找到任何可以支撑住火箭筒和
Find me anything that can sustain heavy RPGs

07:54.150 --> 07:55.210
轻武器的东西
and small arms.

07:55.220 --> 07:56.870
一支美洲豹 一支步行者
A Cougar, a Stryker.

07:57.110 --> 07:58.200
那不可能
Not gonna happen.

07:58.230 --> 08:00.000
我请示过约克中士 但是
I do have a call in to a Sergeant York, but

08:00.010 --> 08:01.440
计划不会改变
Yeah, that's not going to cut it.

08:01.500 --> 08:02.790
打给苏扎梅尔 让他待命
Call Suezamel, put him on standby,

08:02.800 --> 08:04.150
有需要会找他
tell him we might need him.

08:05.210 --> 08:06.300
有问题吗?
Is there a problem?

08:06.310 --> 08:07.850
我们5点就行动?
We're doing this at 5:00?

08:07.910 --> 08:08.890
我们是可以等到晚上
well we could wait until tonight

08:08.900 --> 08:09.950
除非我们的行动够快
when our guys are moving too fast

08:09.960 --> 08:11.070
眼睛够好使
for our night vision to work properly.

08:11.080 --> 08:12.940
干不干随你
You could even tag along if you want.

08:12.950 --> 08:13.900
快去
Get it done.

08:18.300 --> 08:21.490
(疯狂越狱未遂)
Escape Atrevido Disuelto

08:37.690 --> 08:38.730
你好
Hello.

08:38.890 --> 08:42.040
我找詹姆斯·惠斯勒先生的家人
Yes, I'm trying to locate the family of Mr. James Whistler.

08:43.500 --> 08:45.750
我 我是 他妻子
I-I am his I'm his wife.

08:46.220 --> 08:47.360
你是哪位?
Who's calling?

08:47.420 --> 08:48.350
我叫汤米·戴
My name is Tommy Day.

08:48.360 --> 08:51.060
我是惠斯勒先生的房东
I own the apartment building Mr. Whistler rents from.

08:51.180 --> 08:53.050
他房里有根管子坏了
There's been a busted pipe in his unit that's caused

08:53.060 --> 08:55.490
导致邻居家受到损害
some damage to the apartment next door.

08:57.290 --> 08:57.810
不好意思
I'm sorry.

08:57.820 --> 09:00.300
我想你把詹姆斯和其他人弄混了
I think you have confused James with someoneelse.

09:00.970 --> 09:02.870
他没租什么公寓
He's not renting another apartment.

09:02.890 --> 09:05.080
我确定是惠斯勒先生租了我的房子
Oh, I assure you Mr. Whistler is my tenant.

09:05.370 --> 09:07.940
自从他服刑后我就找不到人了
I couldn't find anyone to contact after his conviction,

09:08.010 --> 09:10.360
但是我看到了他的一封话费账单
but when the mail came, I checked his phone bill.

09:10.370 --> 09:12.270
他给这个号码打了很多电话
There were numerous calls to this number.

09:13.280 --> 09:14.870
如果你能过来的话
If you could please come to the apartment,

09:14.880 --> 09:18.120
地址是奥瓦里奥阿贝尔布拉沃40号
the address is 40 AbelBravo in Obarrio,

09:18.190 --> 09:19.500
4单元
Unit 4.

09:23.990 --> 09:25.050
告诉他们英特尔公司说
Tell your men the intel says

09:25.060 --> 09:27.320
巴拿马人无法进入串行存取存储器
the Panamanians have no access to SAM.

09:29.310 --> 09:30.180
喂
Yeah.

09:30.470 --> 09:32.000
有进展了
There's been a development.

09:52.620 --> 09:54.680
又给了我们四天时间
The Company's giving us four more days.

09:56.360 --> 09:57.380
-好的 -问题是
-Okay. -Problem is

09:57.390 --> 10:00.790
我 不知道我们怎么出去
I, uh, I don't know how we're getting out of here.

10:01.130 --> 10:03.640
勒齐或许有办法 我还在等
Lechero might have some ideas, but I'm still waiting

10:03.650 --> 10:04.870
他的消息
to hear from him.

10:06.600 --> 10:08.630
对不起 你现在不方便吗
I'm sorry, is this a bad time for you?

10:09.020 --> 10:11.230
这一天很难熬
It's been an intense 24 hours.

10:11.610 --> 10:12.760
我脑子里很乱
I have things on my mind.

10:12.770 --> 10:16.460
也许和你上一次的探视有关
Yeah, like your last trip to visitation maybe.

10:17.610 --> 10:18.770
怎么 你监视我?
What, you're a spy now?

10:18.780 --> 10:20.650
如果说错了别怪我 不过她看起来
Forgive me if I'm wrong, but she didn't really strike me

10:20.660 --> 10:22.290
不像我喜欢的类型啊
as the girlfriend type.

10:22.620 --> 10:23.890
她是组织派来的
She was Company.

10:24.590 --> 10:26.680
你越狱失败后 她来提醒我
After your failed escape, she came to remind me

10:26.690 --> 10:28.180
我也是在冒险
that I have a stake in this, too,

10:28.570 --> 10:30.470
你似乎忘了这一点
which you seem to have forgotten.

10:30.670 --> 10:32.760
如果你说在筹备另一个越狱计划
So forgive me if I don't jump for joy

10:32.770 --> 10:34.560
别怪我没有兴高采烈
when you say you're working on a plan

10:34.570 --> 10:36.570
因为那个计划可能又会失败
that may very well fail again.

10:38.870 --> 10:39.560
我必须得出去
I've got to get out of here,

10:39.570 --> 10:41.970
无论用什么方法
and it's getting to the point where I don't care how.

10:49.170 --> 10:51.070
明白我的意思了吗
Got what we talked about?

10:51.770 --> 10:53.270
你从没见过我
You never met me.

11:14.970 --> 11:16.270
天哪
Oh, my God.

11:16.370 --> 11:17.970
发生什么事了?
What the hell is going on?

11:18.670 --> 11:19.960
谢尔斯
Shales

11:19.970 --> 11:21.660
奥斯卡·谢尔斯怎么了?
What about Oscar Shales?

11:21.670 --> 11:26.270
他 强奸 杀人 虐待
He raped, killed, tortured.

11:26.870 --> 11:28.160
但我没办法治他罪
I couldn't turn, turn him over

11:28.170 --> 11:31.260
那些混账律师要把他弄出去
to some scumbag lawyer who was just gonna get him off or

11:31.270 --> 11:34.970
不 我只是
or no, no, I just

11:36.570 --> 11:38.170
所以我杀了他
so I killed him.

11:42.170 --> 11:44.570
我感觉 很好
And I felt good.

11:48.970 --> 11:51.170
非常非常好
I felt, I felt really good.

11:52.670 --> 11:55.560
然后你知道吗 我脑海里就一直出现
But then, you know, came the visions

11:55.570 --> 11:57.560
谢尔斯求我放他生路的一幕
of Shales begging for his life,

11:57.570 --> 11:59.170
我摆脱不了
and I couldn't get rid of them,

11:59.270 --> 12:03.670
所以我得靠吃药来保持平静
so I, I got these drugs that kept me on an even keel.

12:05.070 --> 12:06.760
当我到了索纳监狱
And then when I got to Sona,

12:06.770 --> 12:10.670
我拿不到药 所以我不得不
I coul get my pills, so I had to

12:12.670 --> 12:14.470
临时救急
improvise.

12:18.770 --> 12:21.170
要我帮你弄点药吗
Did you want me to get drugs for you?

12:22.470 --> 12:24.960
我确信想让我作证的人
I assume that whoever set this up must think

12:24.970 --> 12:26.970
一定是觉得我还有价值
that I might have some value.

12:29.470 --> 12:32.270
这是你回来找我的原因吧
It's why you came back for me.

12:33.070 --> 12:39.570
我是来帮助一个我敬仰和关心的人
I came here to help a man that I respect and care about.

12:41.570 --> 12:43.570
荣幸之至
And I appreciate that.

12:46.370 --> 12:48.870
但是我现在这个样子没法作证
But I can't testify like this.

12:52.570 --> 12:53.870
求你了
Please

12:57.370 --> 12:58.770
求你了
Please

13:06.070 --> 13:09.170
窗户上都加了一英尺厚的强化钢
One inch of reinforced steel on every window.

13:09.170 --> 13:11.070
没人出的去
Nothing would get through those.

13:11.370 --> 13:12.970
我会找到办法的
I'll figure something out.

13:13.470 --> 13:14.870
我知道你会
I know you will.

13:16.270 --> 13:18.270
听着 刚才很抱歉
Listen, man, I'm sorry about before.

13:18.870 --> 13:20.760
就像我说的 事情变得很紧张了
Like I said, things have been intense.

13:20.770 --> 13:22.970
行动成功太重要了
So much depends on this working out.

13:23.170 --> 13:25.460
我侄子的命也取决于这次的行动
My nephew's life depends on this working.

13:25.470 --> 13:26.970
我知道
I know it does.

13:26.970 --> 13:28.670
我还没问过 他多大了?
I never asked how old is he?

13:29.070 --> 13:30.370
16岁
Sixteen.

13:30.570 --> 13:32.070
天哪
Oh, hell.

13:33.870 --> 13:35.370
叮咚 叮咚
Knock knocka.

13:36.570 --> 13:37.760
你来干嘛?
What do you want?

13:37.770 --> 13:40.360
我? 我只是来把一些东西
Me? I just came by to slip something

13:40.370 --> 13:41.460
扔进你的信箱里
into your mail slot.

13:41.470 --> 13:43.360
是老大给的
It's from El Patron himself,

13:43.370 --> 13:45.470
但是只给你们看
but it was made for your eyes only.

13:45.570 --> 13:46.670
收好了
Grabby.

13:47.470 --> 13:48.560
我看这可不像是一个舞会
That don't look like no invitation

13:48.570 --> 13:50.460
邀请函什么的
to the Sona-Hains Dance.

13:50.470 --> 13:51.860
你和勒齐在策划什么事?
What do you got cooking up with Lechero, huh?

13:51.870 --> 13:53.870
不关你的事 蒂博格
It's none of your business, Theodore.

13:54.970 --> 13:56.260
你想对我保密?
You want to keep secrets?

13:56.270 --> 13:58.560
你当我是一支讨厌虫? 随便你
You want to treat me like a pesky insect? Fine.

13:58.570 --> 14:00.360
给我记住 情报 就像面包屑
Just remember, information, like crumbs,

14:00.370 --> 14:02.870
总会撒落在地上让虫子吃掉的
always trickles down to the vermin on the floor.

14:12.170 --> 14:13.470
4点钟?
4:00?

14:14.570 --> 14:17.970
这是勒齐牢房的草图
It's a sketch of Lechero's quarters.

14:30.870 --> 14:33.360
老实说 如果有房客提前支付一年的房租
To be honest, when a tenant pays a year's rent in advance

14:33.370 --> 14:34.970
也不来住的话
and then gets locked up,

14:35.270 --> 14:36.360
我一般都会把这房子再租出去
I normally rent the place out

14:36.370 --> 14:38.960
赚双倍的钱 不过
and double my money, but, uh,

14:38.970 --> 14:40.570
詹姆斯人不错
James was a good man.

14:41.270 --> 14:43.270
我一直希望他的事情可以有转机
I was hoping things would turn out well for him.

14:47.370 --> 14:49.470
我说 夫人
Look, uh, miss

14:50.370 --> 14:53.360
很多人都会有一些自己的秘密
a lot of guys have a little something on the side.

14:53.370 --> 14:56.060
我是说 这个公寓 无论他带谁来过这里
This apartment, I mean, whoever he brought here,

14:56.070 --> 14:57.870
并不意味着他不爱你
doesn't mean he didn't love ya.

14:59.970 --> 15:03.770
你说你这有詹姆斯的保险单?
You said you have James' insurance paper?

15:04.870 --> 15:06.160
稍等 马上
Right on. Right on.

15:06.170 --> 15:08.070
我去给你拿来
I'll, uh, I'll go get them.

15:30.770 --> 15:32.470
哦 我的天
Oh, God.

15:45.370 --> 15:47.370
那儿还有一扇门
There's another door in here.

15:54.670 --> 15:56.770
"4413"
"4413."

16:17.470 --> 16:19.670
4413 对吧
4413, huh?

16:29.670 --> 16:31.260
那斯科菲尔德怎么办
What about Scofield?

16:31.270 --> 16:32.670
干掉他
Kill him.

16:33.470 --> 16:35.270
如果这个草图不是勒齐给我们的
You know, if Lechero didn't send this,

16:35.770 --> 16:37.970
那么这事就是有人派蒂博格算计我的
T-Bag might be setting me up for someone.

16:38.570 --> 16:40.060
我们从这里出去
I say we get out of here.

16:40.070 --> 16:43.170
迈克 你因为我惹上了这么多麻烦 很抱歉
I'm truly sorry you got caught up in my troubles, Michael.

16:58.000 --> 16:59.300
斯科菲尔德
Scofield.

17:02.000 --> 17:03.800
这儿还有一个密码锁
I take it there's another code.

17:03.900 --> 17:05.290
我是唯一知道的人
I'm the only one that knows it.

17:05.300 --> 17:06.890
对于一个喜欢保密的人
For a man who likes keeping a secret,

17:06.900 --> 17:08.290
选择蒂博格作为送信人
choosing T-Bag as a go-between

17:08.300 --> 17:09.490
可不是一个明智的选择
might not be the smartest move.

17:09.500 --> 17:12.290
是的 不过当他想明白的时候 我们早就跑远了
Yeah, by the time he figures it out, we'll be long gone.

17:12.300 --> 17:14.400
萨米正在回来的路上 走吧
Sammy's on his way back. Let's go.

17:35.200 --> 17:36.500
这是他妈什么?
What the hell's this?

17:37.700 --> 17:39.400
地下通道
Underground tunnel.

17:40.600 --> 17:41.890
原来看守用做
The old administration used it

17:41.900 --> 17:44.100
从A区到B区的通道
to travel between cellblocks A and B.

17:44.900 --> 17:49.000
自从暴动之后 他们把我们都转移到了B区
After the riots, they moved us all to B.

17:49.400 --> 17:51.200
然后当兵的就
And then the soldiers came in,

17:52.000 --> 17:53.500
把这个通道炸了
blew this tunnel up.

18:03.400 --> 18:06.000
看起来有人已经试图打通这些废墟了
Looks like someone already tried to get through the debris.

18:06.200 --> 18:09.200
我可没打算一辈子都待在这里
I never planned to spend my whole life in Sona.

18:09.900 --> 18:12.100
只是没想到这么快就得走了
Just didn't expect it to end so soon.

18:12.800 --> 18:14.400
你是工程师 对吧
You're the engineer, though, right?

18:14.900 --> 18:16.600
我想你能弄条路出去吧?
You can dig our way out of this?

18:16.600 --> 18:19.600
是的 但我需要几个装载机
Yeah, me and a couple of payloaders.

18:19.600 --> 18:20.790
给我听好了
Now, you listen.

18:20.800 --> 18:23.100
你必须得从这里挖出去
You're gonna dig out of this place.

18:23.400 --> 18:27.500
我们不能挖出去 不过我们可以试试向上挖
We're not digging out, but we might be diggin up.

18:40.700 --> 18:42.500
你好 索菲亚
Hello, Sofia.

18:43.500 --> 18:45.400
你好 你是谁
Hello. Who are you?

18:45.500 --> 18:46.900
詹姆斯的一个朋友
Friend of James.

18:47.600 --> 18:48.900
老朋友
Old friend.

18:49.100 --> 18:50.500
他现在不在
Well, he isn't here.

18:52.400 --> 18:53.800
我知道他在哪
I know where he is.

18:58.800 --> 19:01.000
我可知道詹姆斯为什么喜欢你了
I can see why James loves you.

19:01.500 --> 19:03.500
你真漂亮
You are beautiful.

19:03.500 --> 19:05.090
如果你继续到处瞎打探消息
If you keep sticking your nose where

19:05.100 --> 19:06.490
而不乖乖待着的话
it doesn't belong,

19:06.500 --> 19:09.490
我会让他再也见不到你的
I'm gonna make him miss you very, very much.

19:09.500 --> 19:11.600
你知道我的意思了吧
Do you understand what I'm saying to you?

19:13.900 --> 19:15.100
很好
Good.

19:17.600 --> 19:19.300
这个不需要你来操心
You don't need to worry about this.

19:20.000 --> 19:23.700
听清楚了索菲亚 这样你才不会受到伤害
Now listen very carefully to me, Sofia, and you won't get hurt.

19:23.800 --> 19:26.090
我要你回家待着 做做头发
I want you to go home and do your hair

19:26.100 --> 19:27.790
涂好指甲 准备好
and paint your nails and get all ready

19:27.800 --> 19:29.400
等着詹姆斯回家
for when James comes home.

19:29.600 --> 19:31.190
然后你们就幸福地过一辈子
You two will live happily ever after.

19:31.200 --> 19:32.700
你想从他这儿得到什么
What do you want from him?

19:34.900 --> 19:37.100
瞧 你又不听话了
See? You're not listening already.

19:37.600 --> 19:38.690
别插手这事
Don't get in the way,

19:38.700 --> 19:42.100
不然你会很难堪的
or I promise you things will get very bad for you.

19:47.000 --> 19:49.200
你真的很漂亮
You are truly beautiful.

19:52.800 --> 19:54.900
我希望你可以始终这样
I hope you can stay that way.

19:57.400 --> 19:59.100
现在滚吧
Get the hell out of here

20:13.400 --> 20:15.490
好吧 如果我们可以穿过天花板
All right, if we can get through

20:15.500 --> 20:17.590
地基 还有上面的土层
the ceiling, the foundation and the earth on top othat,

20:17.600 --> 20:19.900
我们就可以上到禁入区了
we can make it out into the middle of no-man's-land

20:19.900 --> 20:22.100
然后我们可以在被击中之前到达围栏
and maybe hit the fence before we get shot.

20:22.300 --> 20:24.700
是啊 我们可不想被射死
Yeah. Well, we wouldn't want that.

20:24.800 --> 20:26.700
对的 不过你确实可以挖通 对吧
Yes, but you can dig out, though, right?

20:26.700 --> 20:29.390
根据重力学和索纳地下的沙质情况来看
Based on gravity and the kind of sand that Sona's built on,

20:29.400 --> 20:31.590
我们在挖掘时需要支柱来支撑这个通道
we're gonna need some kind of support brace for the tunnel.

20:31.600 --> 20:33.600
不然的话
Or

20:33.600 --> 20:34.500
不然怎样?
Or what?

20:35.100 --> 20:38.800
不然整个隧道会坍塌 我们就会被活埋
The whole thing collapses and we're buried alive.

20:43.600 --> 20:45.500
大家随便点
Go on and relax, huh?

20:45.700 --> 20:47.000
我去弄点朗姆酒来
I'll get some rum.

20:49.800 --> 20:50.490
这要花多久时间
How long will this take?

20:50.500 --> 20:51.900
大约两天
Maybe two days.

20:52.400 --> 20:54.190
我得上楼去看看 估算我们
I got to get upstairs, estimate exactly where

20:54.200 --> 20:56.600
从隧道出去后到底处于禁入区的什么方位
in no-man's land that tunnel's gonna let out.

21:04.500 --> 21:06.190
你去哪 我正考虑问题呢
Where you going? I'm meditating.

21:06.200 --> 21:08.390
来给克里斯托巴和他的人弄点朗姆酒
Just getng rum for Cristobal and his boys.

21:08.400 --> 21:10.600
朗姆酒? 给他的人
Rum? His boys?

21:10.700 --> 21:12.490
我确实说过愿意见见克里斯托巴
No, I said I'd meet with Cristobal,

21:12.500 --> 21:14.090
但不是一大堆人
not every half-breed in Sona.

21:14.100 --> 21:15.490
不过 他们现在正在上面呢
Well, they up there right now.

21:15.500 --> 21:16.890
那我们走
So, let's go.

21:16.900 --> 21:19.090
-让我给他们弄点朗姆酒吧 -没门
-Let me just get some rum, now. -No, man.

21:19.100 --> 21:20.390
让他们向其他人一样喝啤酒好了
Then drink beer like everyone else.

21:20.400 --> 21:23.190
我说 哥们 给他们点好东西
Look, man, offer them something good.

21:23.200 --> 21:25.000
不要让我难堪
Don't make me look fool.

21:26.400 --> 21:28.000
这酒是我的 萨米
The rum is for me, Sammy.

21:28.900 --> 21:30.000
我说不行
No?

21:30.300 --> 21:31.700
你有意见吗
You have a problem with that?

21:35.200 --> 21:36.300
没意见 先生
No, sir.

21:37.000 --> 21:37.890
很好
Good.

21:37.900 --> 21:39.000
那我们走吧
Let's go.

21:44.900 --> 21:46.200
我们继续干吧
Let's get back to work.

21:51.800 --> 21:54.400
只有勒齐才知道密码
Hey, only Lechero has the code.

21:54.500 --> 21:55.800
我们不需要密码
We don't need a code.

22:00.200 --> 22:01.490
进去
Now, get inside.

22:01.500 --> 22:03.300
在萨米回来之前
before Sammy comes back.

22:10.000 --> 22:11.200
阿历克斯
Alex?

22:16.600 --> 22:17.900
兰探员呢
Where's Agent Lang?

22:19.200 --> 22:20.500
她 不知道
Agent I don't know.

22:20.800 --> 22:23.300
你这是怎么了 发生什么了吗
But what the hell's wrong with you? What's going on?

22:25.400 --> 22:26.590
我有权紧张
I have a right to be nervous.

22:26.600 --> 22:28.290
我的处境很危险 不是吗
My life is on the line, you know?

22:28.300 --> 22:29.600
你说什么呢
What are you talking about?

22:29.600 --> 22:32.390
你以前总是召开现场记者招待会
You have given live press conferences your entire life.

22:32.400 --> 22:34.090
我见过很多次了 你是老手了
I've seen you many times. You're an old pro.

22:34.100 --> 22:35.990
去洗个脸
Now, splash some water on your face.

22:36.000 --> 22:37.890
陪审团让我们现在就去 马上
The panel wants us there right now, immediately.

22:37.900 --> 22:40.000
-什么? -穿好衣服
-What? -Get dressed.

22:40.300 --> 22:40.890
还是你想让我
Or would you rather have me

22:40.900 --> 22:42.600
把你再送回索纳?
drag your ass back to Sona?

22:43.000 --> 22:46.500
洗洗脸 穿上西装 我们现在就走
Water on the face. Get your suit on. We're going.

22:50.900 --> 22:51.790
是 这是苏林斯
Yeah, it's Sullins.

22:51.800 --> 22:53.190
我们马上就出发了
Uh, we're almost ready to move here.

22:53.200 --> 22:54.600
兰到底去哪了
Where the hell is Lang?

22:56.300 --> 22:57.100
不
No.

22:58.200 --> 22:59.100
我们进展如何
Where are we at?

22:59.400 --> 23:00.490
一切就绪
Everything's in place.

23:00.500 --> 23:02.290
不错 我们准备好了
Good. We've done our part.

23:02.300 --> 23:04.700
现在就等惠斯勒了
Now it's time for Whistler to step up and do his.

23:05.300 --> 23:08.400
5点过来 他最好准备好了
Come 5:00, he better be ready.

23:09.500 --> 23:11.290
打通三尺厚的钢筋混凝土
Three feet of concrete and rebar,

23:11.300 --> 23:13.400
和10尺的泥沙
plus ten feet of dirt and sand,

23:13.400 --> 23:14.900
我们就能看见外面了
before we see sky.

23:18.800 --> 23:19.900
你怎么了
Are you all right?

23:21.100 --> 23:22.800
老实说
To be completely honest

23:24.100 --> 23:25.300
不好
no,

23:25.400 --> 23:26.300
一点儿都不
not really.

23:26.400 --> 23:28.790
我不能呆在狭窄的空间里
I have this thing for, uh, confined spaces.

23:28.800 --> 23:30.390
你有幽闭恐怖症?
Are you telling me you're claustrophobic?

23:30.400 --> 23:31.590
从我还是个
Ever since I was a

23:31.600 --> 23:32.390
孩子的时候
boy.

23:32.400 --> 23:34.990
我必须上去
Um, you know, I need to be upstairs.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.390
现在不行
That's not really an option right now.

23:36.400 --> 23:39.390
我真的不能呆在这里
Well, staying here is not really an option for me, either.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.890
振作一下
I suggest you get yourself togetr.

23:40.900 --> 23:42.600
我去透透气
I just need some air.

23:46.600 --> 23:47.790
你到底怎么了
What the hell's the matter with you?

23:47.800 --> 23:50.790
-我得出去透透气 -如果你现在上去
-I need to get out of here; I need air. -Hey, you walk

23:50.800 --> 23:51.990
萨米就在那里
through that door with Sammy on the other side,

23:52.000 --> 23:52.990
你上去就死定了
you'll never need air again.

23:53.000 --> 23:56.900
你不明白的 我得离开这里
You don't understand,I need to get out of here now.

23:57.300 --> 23:58.990
告诉我究竟发生了什么惠斯勒
Why don't you tell me what's really going on here, Whistler?

23:59.000 --> 24:00.690
你干嘛总看表
Why do you keep looking at your watch?

24:00.700 --> 24:02.200
你到底要去哪
What are you really up to?

24:04.400 --> 24:06.600
斯科菲尔德 他们走了 快走
Scofield, the men are gone, let's move.

24:13.600 --> 24:14.390
我想用一下手机
I need your cell phone.

24:14.400 --> 24:15.890
不行 萨米马上就回来了 离开这里
No, Sammy's on his way, get out of here.

24:15.900 --> 24:18.090
-我得打电话给我哥 -不行 手机得放我这
-I have to call my brother. -No, cell phone stays with me. Now,

24:18.100 --> 24:19.100
赶紧离开这儿
get out of here

24:23.200 --> 24:24.690
美国佬 我们得说说清楚
Well, just so that we're clear, Americano,

24:24.700 --> 24:26.890
这房子没通电 没有自来水
she's got no electricity and no running water.

24:26.900 --> 24:30.100
而且屋里没有卫生间 但是林子里可以方便
Septic's out, too, but there's an outhouse in the woods.

24:30.100 --> 24:33.490
-不错 一个月100 -200
It's perfect. A hundred bucks a month. $200.

24:33.500 --> 24:34.900
就100块
A hundred bucks a month.

24:37.100 --> 24:38.100
成交
Deal.

24:38.400 --> 24:40.800
但是不准种毒品
But I don't want growing no drugs on the land.

24:41.100 --> 24:42.500
也不准种大麻
No marijuana.

24:43.900 --> 24:45.000
听见了吗
You got that?

24:52.400 --> 24:54.400
-欢迎回家 朋友 -谢了
-Welcome home, my friend. -Thanks.

24:57.700 --> 24:58.290
哥们儿 如果你现在不想干了
Listen, man, if you want to get out of here,

24:58.300 --> 25:00.900
我会理解的 迈克也会的
I'd get it and Michael would, too.

25:00.900 --> 25:03.690
你已经做了很多了
You've done more than enough.

25:03.700 --> 25:05.900
如果换作我儿子被绑架
If I had a kid in the same situation as your son,

25:06.000 --> 25:07.900
你们兄弟俩会帮我吗
would you and your brother walk out on me?

25:08.500 --> 25:09.400
当然会了
Yeah.

25:11.000 --> 25:12.090
这里就行
Here, this is good.

25:12.100 --> 25:13.100
把它放在这
Put it down there.

25:15.500 --> 25:16.500
拿好
Okay, hold on.

25:19.500 --> 25:20.190
准备好了?
You ready?

25:20.200 --> 25:21.100
是的
Yeah.

25:25.500 --> 25:27.200
我希望这能管用 伙计
I hope this works, papi.

25:29.100 --> 25:31.100
我们走
All right, let's go.

25:35.300 --> 25:36.400
麦格雷迪
McGrady.

25:40.200 --> 25:41.500
帮我个忙
I need your help.

25:41.500 --> 25:43.790
现在不行 我爸爸已经到了 我得出去见他
Not now, bro my father finally got here; I'm gonna go see him.

25:43.800 --> 25:46.400
事实上 我也需要他的帮助
Actually, uh, I need his help, too.

25:48.500 --> 25:49.990
你想让他干什么
What you want from my old man?

25:50.000 --> 25:50.990
我只是想找个信任的人
I just need someone to deliver

25:51.000 --> 25:52.890
能在外面帮我传个消息
a message on the outside, someone I can trust.

25:52.900 --> 25:56.190
不 我爸爸性格很直
Hell, no. My papa's straight as razor blade.

25:56.200 --> 25:57.790
他不想惹事上身
He don't get into kind of trouble like you do.

25:57.800 --> 26:00.100
-不会惹麻烦的 只是打个电话 -不
-It's not trouble, it's just a phone call. -No.

26:01.300 --> 26:02.600
我爱我爸爸
I love my father.

26:03.000 --> 26:05.650
我也爱我哥哥 如果他没有收到消息的话
And I love my brother, and if he doesn't get this message

26:05.650 --> 26:07.400
就会发生可怕的事
something horrible's gonna happen to him.

26:07.800 --> 26:10.190
听着非常不好的事情就会发生
Look something really bad is going on.

26:10.200 --> 26:11.200
求你了
Please.

26:17.200 --> 26:18.300
你好吗 儿子
Hello, son.

26:19.000 --> 26:19.800
爸爸
Papa.

26:20.900 --> 26:22.500
你看起来很帅嘛
You look very handsome.

26:22.800 --> 26:24.200
像你以前在学校照片里的样子
Like your school picture.

26:25.000 --> 26:26.200
谢谢
Gracias.

26:26.300 --> 26:28.500
我帮一个人清扫了房间 换来了这个衬衫
I cleaned a guy's cell for this shirt.

26:30.700 --> 26:31.890
你现在应该在学校的
You should be in school now

26:31.900 --> 26:34.000
-没关系 爸爸 -和你的朋友们
It's okay, Papa. with your friends.

26:36.600 --> 26:38.200
求你了爸爸 别难过
Papa, please, don't get upset.

26:38.800 --> 26:40.300
我在这里也有朋友的
I-I have friends in here.

26:41.600 --> 26:42.490
那个美国人?
The American?

26:42.500 --> 26:45.100
是的 他很好
Yes. He's Nice.

26:45.200 --> 26:47.700
他很守信用 在索纳很少见到这样的人
He keeps his word, it's very rare in Sona.

26:48.700 --> 26:49.800
还有
And, uh

26:50.500 --> 26:51.800
他需要我帮忙
he needs my help.

26:54.400 --> 26:55.800
能见到你真好
Thank God you're here.

26:55.800 --> 26:57.500
我还以为你会早点儿来
Thought you might have come a little earlier,

26:57.900 --> 26:59.390
看看我呢
just to make sure I was okay.

26:59.400 --> 27:02.900
我读了报纸 知道你还好
I read the newspaper I knew you were safe.

27:03.200 --> 27:06.800
我是 至少现在 但你有可能会不安全
I am for now but you might not be.

27:07.400 --> 27:08.800
仔细听我说
Now, listen to me carefully.

27:09.500 --> 27:12.400
答应我今天不要去找林肯·布鲁斯
Promise me you won't go anywhere near Lincoln Burrows today.

27:12.800 --> 27:14.190
-林肯? -真的很危险
-Lincoln? -It's just too dangerous

27:14.200 --> 27:16.600
只要接近他 就会有危险
to be around him, to be with him, to be near him.

27:16.700 --> 27:19.200
回家呆着
Just go home and stay there,

27:20.200 --> 27:22.000
我今天晚上给你打电话
and I will call you tonight.

27:22.700 --> 27:23.690
我只能说这些
That's all I can say.

27:23.700 --> 27:25.000
你明白吗
Do you understand?

27:25.400 --> 27:28.400
-打给我? 从哪打? -你究竟明不明白
-Call me? From where? -Do you understand me?

27:29.400 --> 27:30.190
明白
Yeah.

27:30.200 --> 27:31.300
答应我
Promise me.

27:31.700 --> 27:33.100
大声说出来
Say it out loud.

27:33.600 --> 27:34.700
我保证
I promise.

27:36.300 --> 27:38.100
你在害怕什么?
Why are you so scared?

27:39.000 --> 27:40.800
因为我不能让你受到伤害
Because I can't have you get hurt.

27:43.000 --> 27:47.600
因为我爱你胜过一切
Because I love you more than anything in the world.

27:49.200 --> 27:50.200
是吗?
Do you?

27:52.100 --> 27:53.300
当然
Yeah.

27:55.400 --> 27:55.890
詹姆斯
James,

27:55.900 --> 27:57.200
今天我接到一个电话
I got a call today

27:57.300 --> 27:59.500
他说是你的房东
from a man who said he's your landlord.

28:00.700 --> 28:02.500
另一个公寓的
Talking about another apartment.

28:03.900 --> 28:05.400
我要给他回话吗?
Should I call him back?

28:05.800 --> 28:07.400
肯定是打错了
Must have been a wrong number.

28:07.600 --> 28:09.300
他指名道姓要找你
He asked for you by name.

28:09.400 --> 28:10.900
他一定是糊涂了
The man is clearly confused.

28:10.900 --> 28:13.100
我不知道什么另一个公寓
I don't know anything about another apartment.

28:14.200 --> 28:15.200
索菲亚
Sofia,

28:15.200 --> 28:17.900
我只知道你得离林肯远点
all I know is that you've got to stay away from Lincoln.

28:19.500 --> 28:20.600
拜托了
Please.

28:22.100 --> 28:23.600
好的 詹姆斯
Okay, James.

28:24.600 --> 28:25.900
我会等你的电话
I'll wait for your call.

28:32.300 --> 28:33.400
看
Here.

28:34.100 --> 28:35.500
我给你带了这个
I have this.

28:36.300 --> 28:37.600
我不想看
I don't want to see it.

28:39.900 --> 28:41.390
我会把它跟其他的放在一起
I'll put it with the others.

28:41.400 --> 28:42.700
我回不了家了
I'm not coming home.

28:43.700 --> 28:45.000
接受现实吧
Accept that.

28:50.000 --> 28:51.200
你该走了
You should go.

28:53.300 --> 28:54.900
记得替我朋友打电话
Make that call for my friend.

29:00.800 --> 29:02.200
生日快乐 儿子
Happy birthday, son.

29:15.400 --> 29:16.590
也许我们应该弄些锁
Maybe we should pick up some locks

29:16.600 --> 29:18.990
-把那房子锁起来 -不能让它有所改变
and secure the house. It can't have anything new on it.

29:19.000 --> 29:20.800
那地方得弄成像是废弃的
The place needs to look abandoned.

29:23.200 --> 29:24.590
喂
Yeah?

29:24.600 --> 29:26.100
我给你带条口信
I have a message for you.

29:26.500 --> 29:28.000
不要回家吃晚饭
Don't come home for dinner.

29:28.000 --> 29:29.000
你是谁
Who is this?

29:29.100 --> 29:30.290
我只负责告诉你
I'm supposed to tell you,

29:30.300 --> 29:32.000
不要回家吃晚饭
don't come home for dinner.

29:33.900 --> 29:34.800
什么?
What?

29:35.000 --> 29:36.090
小时候 我和迈克
When me and Mikey were kids,

29:36.100 --> 29:37.990
有一套暗号 用来对付
we had a code when Social Services

29:38.000 --> 29:39.900
那些想把我关进少管所的人
were trying to get me into juvie.

29:40.500 --> 29:42.100
这是他让我小心的暗号
He's telling me to watch my back.

29:47.600 --> 29:48.690
你在这干什么呢
What the hell are you doing here?

29:48.700 --> 29:50.690
你怎么不回我电话 也不还我车?
Why haven't you returned my calls or my car?

29:50.700 --> 29:51.700
你看见他了吗
You have him?

29:52.100 --> 29:54.800
他刚回酒店
Yeah, he just arrived back at his hotel.

29:55.000 --> 29:56.900
但是惠斯勒的女朋友也找到他了
But Whistler's girl tracked him down.

29:57.200 --> 29:57.890
她正在跟
And she's talking

29:57.900 --> 29:59.900
林肯和那个墨西哥人说话
to Lincoln and the Mexican.

30:00.400 --> 30:02.900
她昨天看到了那些东西 一定会让事情复杂化
After what she saw today, she could be complicating things.

30:03.100 --> 30:04.200
你警告她了吗
You have a directive?

30:04.900 --> 30:05.900
我说过了
I warned her.

30:06.400 --> 30:07.390
把他们都干掉
Take them all out.

30:07.400 --> 30:08.590
那惠斯勒会怎样?
What will Whistler say?

30:08.600 --> 30:11.000
我说把他们都干掉
I said take them all out

30:17.500 --> 30:18.990
我不关心你男朋友
I don't care about your boyfriend's apartment

30:19.000 --> 30:20.490
在那里的公寓 不关我的事
on the side, I just don't care.

30:20.500 --> 30:21.790
不 我去了那里
No, I went there.

30:21.800 --> 30:23.400
然后一个女人来了
And a woman showed up;

30:23.500 --> 30:24.700
她威胁我
she threatened me.

30:25.000 --> 30:26.500
她认识詹姆斯
She knows James.

30:27.700 --> 30:28.590
苏珊
Susan.

30:28.600 --> 30:29.600
你认识她?
You know her?

30:29.600 --> 30:31.500
LJ就在她手上
She's the one who has LJ.

30:33.400 --> 30:35.200
她拿走了我发现的一些东西
Well, she took something I found,

30:35.500 --> 30:36.700
一本护照
a passport.

30:37.000 --> 30:39.200
上面有詹姆斯的照片和生日
It had James' picture and birthday

30:39.400 --> 30:41.200
但名字写的是格雷·米勒
but his name said Gary Miller.

30:41.500 --> 30:43.090
林肯我不明白是怎么回事
Lincoln, I don't know what's going on.

30:43.100 --> 30:43.890
我告诉你怎么回事
I'll tell you what's going on

30:43.900 --> 30:44.690
你男朋友是个骗子
your boyfriend's a liar.

30:44.700 --> 30:46.290
我一早就说过了
I told you that from the start.

30:46.300 --> 30:48.600
詹姆斯让我今天离你远点
James told me to stay away from you today,

30:48.800 --> 30:50.100
因为会很危险
that it was dangerous.

30:50.900 --> 30:51.800
我们上
Let's go.

31:05.000 --> 31:06.000
等一下
Pronto.

31:06.000 --> 31:07.690
我要找迈克·斯科菲尔德
I need to speak to Michael Scofield.

31:07.700 --> 31:08.900
我是他哥哥
I'm his brother.

31:10.000 --> 31:11.500
你怎么知道这个号码的
How you get this number?

31:13.900 --> 31:15.290
他几天前给我打过电话
He called a few days back.

31:15.300 --> 31:16.190
我没接
I-I didn't answer.

31:16.200 --> 31:18.900
听着 我现在需要跟他讲话
But, listen, I-I need to speak to him now.

31:28.600 --> 31:29.900
跟上
Let's go.

31:30.000 --> 31:34.100
你绝对猜不到 是迈克·斯科菲尔德的哥哥
You'll never guess Michael Scofield's brother.

31:34.600 --> 31:35.800
谁给我打电话
Who calls me

31:36.400 --> 31:37.900
我打给谁
and who I call,

31:38.300 --> 31:39.900
都是我的事
is my business.

31:45.900 --> 31:46.790
你的朋友呢
Where are your friends?

31:46.800 --> 31:47.290
我不知道
I don't know.

31:47.300 --> 31:48.690
在哪里
Where are your friends?

31:48.700 --> 31:51.400
我不知道 求你别开枪
I don't know, Please don't shoot. Please.

31:52.600 --> 31:53.700
扔掉枪
Drop it.

31:54.000 --> 31:55.900
你为什么纠缠不休?
Why are you coming after this?

32:14.600 --> 32:17.000
一切又重演了是吗 林肯
Different day, same problem, huh, Lincoln?

32:17.000 --> 32:19.090
那天LJ也这样在我手里 你知道后果的
You know how it turned out when LJ was in this position,

32:19.100 --> 32:21.000
今天也是一样
and today is no different

32:22.200 --> 32:25.500
所以乖乖地放下枪
so be a good boy and put down the gun.

32:27.600 --> 32:29.090
快点 林肯
Come on, Linc.

32:29.100 --> 32:31.300
我知道你已经有过次教训了
I know you've learned your lesson.

32:37.000 --> 32:39.400
你说得对 我是有了
You're right, I have.

32:55.600 --> 32:56.490
我郑重声明
For the record,

32:56.500 --> 32:58.490
这是美国政府要求举行的
this is an international hearing,

32:58.500 --> 33:00.790
一次国际听证会
requested by the United States government,

33:00.800 --> 33:06.100
目的是听取阿历克斯·马宏先生的证词
for the purpose of hearing testimony from one Mr. Alexander Mahone.

33:06.900 --> 33:08.700
你不是开玩笑吧
You gotta be kidding me.

33:08.800 --> 33:10.400
马宏先生
So, Mr. Mahone,

33:10.600 --> 33:13.090
你第一次接触
when were you first contacted by anyone

33:13.100 --> 33:16.400
这个所谓的"组织"是什么时候
from the group referred to the Company?

33:16.900 --> 33:18.400
他们告诉我
They told me

33:19.500 --> 33:23.490
如果我不把福克斯河越狱的8个人都杀掉
that if I didn't kill every one of the Fox River Eight,

33:23.500 --> 33:25.100
他们就会来对付我
that they would come after me.

33:25.100 --> 33:27.190
那些人都跟斯科菲尔德一起
They had all worked with-with Scofield

33:27.200 --> 33:28.890
执行了越狱计划
on-on-on the escape,

33:28.900 --> 33:31.590
所以"组织"不确定他们到底知道了什么
so the Company wasn't sure what they knew.

33:31.600 --> 33:33.590
马宏先生 请你
Mr. Mahone, I'm going to ask you

33:33.600 --> 33:36.700
不要答非所问
to please keep your answer related to the question.

33:36.700 --> 33:37.890
这些其实都互有关联的
It's-it's all connected.

33:37.900 --> 33:40.000
它是个 是张复杂的大网
It's just it's-it's a web.

33:40.800 --> 33:43.600
我身陷在这个网里
And-and it's a web that I got caught in.

33:43.700 --> 33:45.890
林肯·布鲁斯被卷入其中
And-and Lincoln Burrows got caught in,

33:45.900 --> 33:47.090
迈克·斯科菲尔德也是
and Michael Scofield got caught in.

33:47.100 --> 33:48.890
我如果可以
I, if I may,

33:48.900 --> 33:50.490
我想马宏先生是想说
I think what Mr. Mahone

33:50.500 --> 33:51.590
-我们都像苍蝇一样 -我是说
-We're all just like flies -was trying to say

33:51.600 --> 33:52.790
谢谢你 苏林斯先生
Thank you, Mr. Sullins,

33:52.800 --> 33:54.700
但我们要听的是马宏先生的证词
but we're here to hear from Mr. Mahone.

33:55.400 --> 33:57.100
现在 我们再来一次
Now, we're going to try this again.

33:57.100 --> 33:58.790
你什么时候第一次接触到
When were you first contacted

33:58.800 --> 34:00.400
组织?
by the Company?

34:03.000 --> 34:04.400
我不能说
I cannot say.

34:05.800 --> 34:06.900
你知道
You know

34:07.200 --> 34:09.090
他们什么时候联络你 或者
they could be in contact with you or-or-or

34:09.100 --> 34:11.890
什么时候你被联络 都是未知的
you could be in contact with them, you'd never know.

34:11.900 --> 34:16.200
他们也许现在正在联络我们
It's-it's they could be in contact with us right now.

34:16.300 --> 34:17.100
我知道
I know

34:17.400 --> 34:18.190
这听起来太疯狂了 不是么?
it sounds crazy, right?

34:18.200 --> 34:19.590
简直疯了
It's crazy and

34:19.600 --> 34:23.300
但这很有可能 而事实上
and it would be, except for the simple fact that

34:23.400 --> 34:24.600
的确如此
It's true.

34:24.600 --> 34:26.590
我为之卖命的政府
The government that I had dedicated my life to

34:26.600 --> 34:30.000
操纵和威逼我
Manipulate and extorted me.

34:30.500 --> 34:31.700
并勒索我
Blackmailed me.

34:33.800 --> 34:35.700
所以我才为他们杀人
So that I would kill for them.

34:36.600 --> 34:38.600
我所做的一切都是他们逼的
And I did the things that they made me do

34:40.500 --> 34:42.100
因为我要保护我的家人
so I could protect my family.

34:45.300 --> 34:46.200
所以
And so

34:50.400 --> 34:52.000
我想回家
I would like to go home.

34:56.300 --> 34:58.000
我能回家么?
So can I do that, please?

35:06.600 --> 35:07.900
你去哪了?
Where have you been?

35:08.100 --> 35:08.690
我去找了
I came looking

35:08.700 --> 35:11.400
能支撑地道的废铁
for scrap metal for the support brace for the tunnel.

35:11.600 --> 35:12.500
当真?
Really?

35:14.700 --> 35:16.390
我看来上面挺挤的
Looks like a pretty tight squeeze up there.

35:16.400 --> 35:17.790
你肯定那里有充足的氧气
You sure there's enough fresh air,

35:17.800 --> 35:19.890
还是只有幽闭病人才会来这种地方?
or does the claustrophobia come and go?

35:19.900 --> 35:23.990
为什么总是如此不信任别人呢?
What's it like going through life always distrustful?

35:24.000 --> 35:25.190
你告诉我 詹姆斯
You tell me, James.

35:25.200 --> 35:27.790
不想打断你们的争吵 先生们
Hate to break up the brouhaha, gentlemen,

35:27.800 --> 35:29.800
但勒齐想见你
but Lechero would like to see you.

35:30.200 --> 35:32.700
想和你聊聊你大哥的事
Says it has something to do with your big brother.

35:45.700 --> 35:47.600
让我们单独待会好吗 蒂博格?
Give us a moment, will you, Teodoro?

35:58.900 --> 36:02.600
如果你哥再给我打电话
If your brother should ever call my cell phone again,

36:03.400 --> 36:05.400
告诉他你会因此付出代价的
you tell him you're the one that's gonna pay.

36:19.600 --> 36:20.590
喂
Yeah?

36:20.600 --> 36:22.190
-你收到消息了 -是的 你是对的
-You got the message. -Yeah, you were right.

36:22.200 --> 36:23.800
他们刚想把我们干掉呢
They just tried to take us out.

36:23.900 --> 36:24.700
我知道
I know.

36:25.000 --> 36:26.490
组织的人曾来探视过惠斯勒
Whistler got a visit from the Company.

36:26.500 --> 36:28.290
从那之后他行为就很反常
He's been acting strange ever since.

36:28.300 --> 36:29.590
林肯 我告诉你 肯定出事了
I'm telling you, Linc, something's up.

36:29.600 --> 36:30.990
兄弟 还有比行为反常更严重的
Doing more than acting strange, man.

36:31.000 --> 36:32.090
他告诉索菲亚别接近我
He just told Sofia not to be

36:32.100 --> 36:33.900
因为这很危险
near me 'cause it's dangerous.

36:35.100 --> 36:36.900
组织盯上我们了
The Company's coming after us.

36:39.300 --> 36:41.000
他们不再需要我们了
They don't need us anymore.

36:41.800 --> 36:42.900
准备行动
Here we go.

36:44.800 --> 36:46.600
他们要自己动手帮他越狱了
They're breaking him out on their own.

36:54.500 --> 36:56.290
我们距离目标100码
We're 100 yards from the target.

36:56.300 --> 36:58.600
保持警惕 行动要快
Keep your eyes open. Let's get in and out fast.

37:01.400 --> 37:02.200
来吧
Come on

37:11.700 --> 37:13.400
糟了
Damn

37:30.200 --> 37:31.100
快点
Come on

37:31.900 --> 37:33.400
快点 加把劲
Come on Keep it coming

37:35.300 --> 37:36.700
快啊
Come on Hey

37:42.400 --> 37:43.990
我看到了一架直升机和两名狱徒
I've got a helicopter and two inmates.

37:44.000 --> 37:47.500
我看不清他们的脸 但他们在屋顶
I can't make out their faces, but they're on the roof

37:59.500 --> 38:00.700
快啊
Come on

38:35.300 --> 38:36.600
看不清楚
Can't get a clean shot

38:37.500 --> 38:39.100
我降低高度 带他们走
I'll get lower, take 'em out

38:41.400 --> 38:43.600
是斯科菲尔德和惠斯勒在屋顶上吗
Is that Scofield on the roof with Whistler?

38:46.700 --> 38:49.100
毫无疑问
Is that really a question?

38:55.800 --> 38:57.390
他死定了
He's supposed to be dead.

38:57.400 --> 38:58.900
有人中枪 有人中枪
Man down. Man down.

39:05.800 --> 39:07.100
快走 我要掉下去了
Let go I'm slipping.

39:10.100 --> 39:13.000
惠斯勒掉下去了 行动中止 行动中止
We lost Whistler. Abort. Abort.

39:13.300 --> 39:14.190
任务失败
Mission failure.

39:14.200 --> 39:16.000
马上返回一号基地
Return to Base One immediately.

40:48.100 --> 40:49.500
阿历克斯
Alex

40:50.400 --> 40:51.700
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

40:52.900 --> 40:55.100
我不得不把你送回索纳监狱
I'm going to have to take you back to Sona.

41:32.800 --> 41:34.300
你 起来
You, get up.

41:34.600 --> 41:35.500
走
Vamos

41:44.200 --> 41:45.500
斯科菲尔德先生
Mr. Scofield,

41:47.100 --> 41:49.890
两天内发生了两起越狱未遂事件
there have been two escape attempts in the past two days.

41:49.900 --> 41:52.690
我相信这不是偶然
Somehow I don't think it's a coincidence

41:52.700 --> 41:55.700
都发生在你来后不久
that you arrived shortly before they happened.

41:56.700 --> 41:58.400
我与此事无关
I had nothing to do with that.

42:03.200 --> 42:06.100
你在索纳惹事太多
You've caused too many problems here in Sona,

42:06.900 --> 42:09.400
或许你不该留在索纳
so maybe you shouldn't be here in Sona.

42:10.900 --> 42:12.100
把他带走
Get him out.

42:14.800 --> 42:16.600
和索纳说再见吧 斯科菲尔德先生
Say good-bye to Sona, Mr. Scofield.
